explanations.description: The token "Jud" or its extended forms often refer to names or concepts with Judeo-Christian roots, like "Judaea", "Judeo-Christian", "Judith", "Judas", or "Jude", and sometimes appear as part of proper nouns, surnames, or in references to biblical contexts.
